  "code": "%%{Health_Sync}}}%%\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [Health_Sync] --> IDLE\n    IDLE --> FETCH: Kick-off\n    FETCH --> PARSE: Complete\n    PARSE --> ARB_READ: Valid\n    PARSE --> ERROR: Invalid\n    ARB_READ --> READ: Grant\n    READ --> ARB_WRITE: Complete\n    ARB_WRITE --> WRITE: Grant\n    WRITE --> CHAIN: Complete\n    CHAIN --> FETCH: Next\n    CHAIN --> COMPLETE: Last\n    COMPLETE --> IDLE: IRQ sent\n    ERROR --> IDLE: SW clear\n",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Health_Sync模块的状态机，核心是从IDLE开始，收到Kick-off后进入FETCH取数据，然后PARSE解析。PARSE之后要分支：Valid的话走ARB_READ去仲裁读，Invalid直接进ERROR。",
