      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PARSE到ARB_READ的条件是Valid，到ERROR是Invalid。那ARB_READ之后呢？Grant之后进入READ状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "Grant"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，READ完成后进入ARB_WRITE，Grant之后到WRITE。WRITE完成就到CHAIN状态，这里要处理链式传输：不是最后一包就Next回到FETCH，最后一包就Last到COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
